function halfArrowRight(r=5,o="#"){for(let n=0;n<r;n++)return""+o}function halfArrowLeft(r=5,o="#",n=" "){for(var t=0;t<r;t+=1){for(var f="",e=r-(t+1),i=0;e>0;)f+=n,e-=1;for(;i<t+1;)f+=o,i+=1;return f}}function secondHalfLeft(r=5,o="#",n=" "){for(var t=0;t<r;t+=1){for(var f="",e=r-(t+1),i=r-e;i>0;)f=n+f,i-=1;for(;e>0;)f+=o,e-=1;return f}}function arrowRight(r=5,o="#",n=" "){halfArrowRight(r,o),halfArrowLeft(5,n,o)}function arrowLeft(r=5,o="#",n=" "){halfArrowLeft(r,o,n),secondHalfLeft(r,o,n)}function ArrowInput(r){console.log(r),r.innerHTML='<div class="row">\n    <div class="input-field col s6">\n      <input value="Lines" id="lines" type="text" class="validate">\n      <input value="Symbol" id="symbol" type="text" class="validate">\n    </div>\n  </div>'}console.log("it works");